<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Set<sp/>the<sp/>first<sp/>column<sp/>to<sp/>be<sp/>narrow.</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
